mainPackage

Class Maze

  • java.lang.Object
    • mainPackage.Maze

  • public class Maze
extends java.lang.Object
    Maze class reprezents a board of cells that have some properties like wall cells or free cells. It has a two-dimensional array of cells and some data about the height and width of the maze and also the position of enter portal.
    Author:
    razvan

    • Method Detail

      • getMazeFromFile

        public void getMazeFromFile(java.lang.String inputFile)
        Get the content of the file and initialize the maze array. It uses a factory to "guess" the type of the cells when building the maze array. Starting position is also set to the position of InPortalCell cell.
        Parameters:
        inputFile - the name of the input file
        See Also:
        CellFactory.createCell(java.lang.String)
